{
  "stem": "3631.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the concentration camps in general?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew there were concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew there was a large ghetto in-- in Warsaw, of course, which was just a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Otherwise I do not really remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew that the concentration camp in Plaszow was being built.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I talk about this now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Jewish Council had a very difficult role.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They formed them, as I have in one of my papers that I have, the gestapo, or the Jewish-- the German authorities formed them to protect the interests of the Jewish population-- I'll put this in quotation marks-- and also to make sure that the Jewish population followed the-- [INAUDIBLE] orders of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish Judenrat, as it called, was-- I think consisted of 25 people in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of them were prominent-- prominent business people or-- or education-- education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember, the one-- the first president that the Judenrat had was a Professor [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bieberstein, ?] who was a highly respected teacher or professor or something, and his vice-president was a-- was an attorney-- well-respected people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Without a Judenrat, there would have been complete chaos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For instance, we had a-- a-- a housing department.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we moved into the ghetto, there were, I don't know, 30 or 40,000 Jews had to be squeezed in a room for 7,000 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, somebody had to tell them where they could-- where to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It had to be allocated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was the-- the work-- labor department, as we could call it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was like a city.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
